<section class="security" id="security">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="security-header">
      <h1>Government-Grade Intelligence.<br>Zero-Trust Architecture.</h1>
      <p>At The Performa Group, we've spent 20 years building the software that runs government. Scotty is built on that same foundation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="arch-cards">
      <div class="arch-card">
        <div class="arch-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="20" stroke="#BE2332" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><rect x="18" y="20" width="12" height="10" rx="2" stroke="#BE2332" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path d="M20 20v-4a4 4 0 018 0v4" stroke="#BE2332" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Private AI Instances</h3>
        <p>Your data is never used to train public models. We deploy "Siloed Intelligence" where your agency's data remains in an isolated, encrypted environment only your authorized staff can access.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-card">
        <div class="arch-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="20" stroke="#BE2332" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path d="M24 10l12 8v12c0 6-12 10-12 10S12 36 12 30V18z" stroke="#BE2332" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path d="M18 25l4 4 8-8" stroke="#BE2332" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Compliance First</h3>
        <p>Designed to meet FedRAMP and NIST standards. AES-256 encryption at rest and TLS 1.3 in transit ensures your financial records are more secure with us than on an internal legacy server.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-card">
        <div class="arch-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="20" stroke="#BE2332" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><rect x="14" y="16" width="20" height="16" rx="2" stroke="#BE2332" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/><path d="M14 22h20M22 22v10" stroke="#BE2332" stroke-width="1.5"/><circle cx="18" cy="19" r="1" fill="#BE2332"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Data Sovereignty</h3>
        <p>All data processed and stored exclusively in the United States, in FedRAMP-compliant data centers. Full domestic control. Role-based access control for every user and endpoint.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

